DMS - Database Migration Service
- Resilient and self healing
- Data remains available after migration
- Supports: Homogeneous and Heterogeneous Migrations.
- Continuous Data Replication using CDC
- EC2 instance to perform the replication task.

Sources
- OnPremise, Aurora, RDS, Azure SQL Database 
Destination
- OnPremise and EC2 instances. RDS, Redshift, DynamoDB, S3, ElasticSearch,
Kinesis, DocumentDB.

